QuestData.Title: Owlcat Soul
QuestData.Description: <The Owlcat Soul is a curious trickster, a beast of many parts working together in a playful balance, always seeking the next challenge. The shape of the owlcat will be yours to call upon.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Owlcat Soul to Lady Muunn in the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Bring the Owlcat Soul to Lady Muunn in the Heart of the Forest.
